@node errstr "STRING ERROR"

A string was not properly delimited.  Each string should start and end with
a  '"'  symbol,  eg.   "fred", "bill" etc.  If you miss out a '"' then this
error will occur. Simply fic the string and all will be well.
@endnode

@node res "RESIZING COLUMNS REFERENCE"

Simply move the mouse to the gap between two column labels and hold the left
mouse  button down.  You should find you are able to move the mouse left and
right and the column width changes as you do it.

Example:

------- ------
  A   | |    B
------- ------
       \
        \Click the mouse between here and hold
@endnode
